Getting audio working on Hp 350 g2

The patches will work for El Capitain ALC282

step 1: install the Patched AppleHDA.kext using a kext utility 

step 2: add patchs "Audio Layout 12" Make sure the layout-id is 28: example = "layout-id", Buffer() { 28, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00 },
"IRQ Fix" to DSDT
(make sure to add DSDT to EFI/Clover/Acpi/Patched)

Step 3: restart



These patches are from RehabMan 
